        {
          "id": "fasten-unfasten-button",
          "title": "Fasten Button",
          "shortDescription": "Button a button on a buttoning board.",
          "description": "Button a button on a buttoning board.",
          "justification": "Fasten Button evaluates a system's ability to perform precision manipulation under tight geometric constraints involving both rigid and deformable components. The task requires quasistatic direct manipulation of a small rigid object whose dimensions are significantly smaller than those of the hand while interacting with a deformable buttonhole. The task exhibits high constraint complexity, as successful completion depends on satisfying multiple geometric constraints simultaneously while maintaining stable contact with the button and fabric. It also involves substantial constraint change, progressing from free-space manipulation to contact with the buttonhole, partial insertion, and eventual passage through the fabric. The interaction requires careful coordination of fingertip forces and object pose throughout the manipulation sequence, and small positioning errors can lead to task failure. More broadly, button fastening serves as a representative benchmark for fine manipulation tasks encountered in dressing, garment handling, and other activities that require precise interaction with small everyday objects.",
          "items": [
            {
              "item": "Buttoning board",
              "quantity": 1,
              "specification": "Buttoning board",
              "link": "https://www.amazon.com/MONTESSORI-OUTLET-Buttoning-Frame-Buttons/dp/B07SZ6NV1M/ref=sr_1_1_sspa?dib=eyJ2IjoiMSJ9.4AWI2-dVREEyGCNyw3aQD0cEPmhbwUcv3NsBaTrQD1_WFfpga9o7j4r-asA6V5Hc3gXy5rwNQg9XHqwmg-iRwd4RyG-FMu3cMYPaJyTR4eobqYigGEY4AhRkcj5NKk_W-3wFdaW3o_mGXRvCHhJU4wS2j5xA0IhcCfZppFfTJdkrVPn-Est_FE1O4WT9GUM1lFZjDvzXl9mvP77PPykAuSYrkpeDjTITMD3hF3nl9fHRnDYxa1ssjSHaUdOsFKDugJucRGGavSyjH3A0C85iuUdPkyT2FqLbDFKMosppvWU.r7GHGZ09kulmp1p9bUaQXORMTKwuJbIp0anAaW2leK4&dib_tag=se&keywords=button%2Bpractice%2Boccupational%2Btherapy&qid=1784511411&sr=8-1-spons&sp_csd=d2lkZ2V0TmFtZT1zcF9hdGY&th=1"
            },
